Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:24.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, go back to your mom's place, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:28.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still no match for the G Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My next prey... is an unfamiliar face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:43.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be enough to entertain me for a little while, Crimson Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She is constantly accelerating and preventing me from catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I ran into a crazy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.96,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like this'll be one night that neither of us will forget, right, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:18.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:23.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two cars are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:25.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:36.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's speeding up at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What lies ahead is a series of unpredictable left and right turns, known as the Yagami Winding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Door of Death that has swallowed countless drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have no regard for her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.05,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless... she's a true soul reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul reaper's scythe is the phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.82,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This joke isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you straight to the depths of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.10,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She yielded the path?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she become unable to endure the sea's wind blowing from the right anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:20.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your light frame became a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The... The morning sun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment of sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.97,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She planned this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.89,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still someone like you in Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I still cannot graduate from the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.24,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:05.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S--Sorry, Sui, I wanted to feel like I was a part of the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your muttering in the back is annoying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get a license if you want to drive so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.35,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that we made it in time for the first sunrise of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
