Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:15.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yakumo! It fits perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show it to Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:21.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Karasuma-kun will go to the first temple visit of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K--Karasuma-kun, Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me this year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year to you too, Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your kimono suits you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.22,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:36.97,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were this beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O--Oh, you're always joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.76,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:01.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N--Nee-san? Wait a minute. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san! Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.71,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.71,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:16.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally... I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be together from now on, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y--You've finally accepted my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.35,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if this is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it {\i1}was{\i0} a dream. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.35,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of first dream of the year was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:51.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the first dream of the year will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the dream I just had...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then it's time to go pray at the first temple visit of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.54,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, something very nice just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the promised bra steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what swimsuit sumo is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no understatement to say that this is a fight for which the girls put everything on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko-san. Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.23,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year. Take care of me this year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Me too! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.35,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there are so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.22,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to find where Miko-chan's performance is located...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Tsukamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:55.37,TL NOTES,(07,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Left Stand: Starch Syrup
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:55.37,TL NOTES,(07,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Right Stand: Fortune Lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. It's hard to move in a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's hard to move! Hahahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A--Are you here to visit the temple, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:58.29,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if it's okay with you, do you want to go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what's this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't something slightly wrong, God?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with the dream coming true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.51,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Go help you," you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Suou Group is putting on a performance here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.72,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.05,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll probably work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.75,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crowded no matter where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san, watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.15,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, thank you, Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to be this happy on New Year's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought that I would go to the first temple visit with Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma, you bastard. I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today will become the anniversary of your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:59.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Suou Group is about to put on a performance, but something came up and I have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take my place until I get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.21,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh. So Harima-kun is the type of person who forgets previous debts once the New Year rolls around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, take care of me this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take care of me," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got things to take care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.54,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's done with two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the guy in the back didn't wait long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go. Sorry for making you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Wait a minute! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! I'd like to know that myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:45.06,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that Mikoto... Stirring things up so early in the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have accepted this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm doing this, Tenma-chan and Karasuma are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.06,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It just moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.08,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you kids come to see the lion dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom told me to come and get bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.15,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.05,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Work with me until Mikoto comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, don't act all high and mighty, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They talk in lion dances, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They have quarrels, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting better, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what good are sacred teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a lion dance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really feels like New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kousuke, why don't you go get bitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? N--No thanks, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It eats people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:11.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! There are beasts like that in Japan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing these!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H--Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.54,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:29.52,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: The lion dance originated in China but other Asian cultures have their own variations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:29.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a wild beast! This is a traditional Japanese event called the lion dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why does it bite people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:40.96,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been said that good things will happen to you if you get bitten by the lion in the lion dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good already happened to you, didn't it, Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to me, you managed to come to the first temple visit with Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:57.15,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Tch, if things went properly, I would be all love-love with Tenma-chan right now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.60,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I had such a good dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Is that true, Karasuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:09.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--That's... Tenma-chan! And Karasuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.22,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to save Tenma-chan from Karasuma's evil grasp right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are too many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:22.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Look, look, Karasuma-kun! The lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:26.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's so big! This is my first time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan... You're too cute after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:35.23,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! If I bite Tenma-chan, we can secretly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun...
