Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret love inside a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I got bitten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori-san, good things will happen to you this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Harim--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I--Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:08.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! After getting bitten so much, you'll have a great year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O--Oh crap. It'll be too late if they reach the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.72,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lion dance is supposed to go on the streets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:22.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The visitors seem happy, so do you want to go outside for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I--I guess so, if that's better...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Now that it's been decided, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-chan, don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:45.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I get the feeling that we're getting weird glances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.51,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What will be your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really great, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening, Hige?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched fireworks with everyone last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, that Karasuma bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.51,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:45.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it, Karasuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will look great with your kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your kimono suits you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--Thank you, Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me this year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm basically finished over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then come do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.97,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is one huge kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:56.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:09.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why do I have to go through this on New Year's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been apologizing to you the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hige.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:18.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me this year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:24.76,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:29.92,Signs,(16,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\an7\fs45\shad0\c&H6B6BF2&\3c&H4E53A2&\fnakbar\pos(460,-5)}Kite Flying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! They're all up so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of different kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:42.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to participate, too. Can you lend me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.10,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You should be able to fly a kite on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kite that can't be flown by one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it stands out, it'll be good for the reputation of our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll score a point against Tougou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Allow me to aid you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:04.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's quite the attitude from someone who hasn't paid this month's rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.87,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mikoto, is that samurai-like one a kite as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.58,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: A "yakkodako" is a kite that is shaped like a footman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a type of kite called the yakkodako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the one over there is up pretty high too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are up pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing! They're battling kites!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:31.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. It just so happens that I felt like settling my score with you this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, don't start playing their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a blockhead as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He landed a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.22,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that was Takano-kun just now--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he went for a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:54.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wow! It's a big battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:17:59.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that! You should be the one stepping down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takano-kun, the time has come to use "that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Harima. From three times the normal height.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he attempting to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With three times the normal amount of rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Sure kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.80,Signs,(18,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\fs35\c&H62A3F0&\an7\shad0\3c&H2D66A8&\fnakbar\pos(130,6)}A Hundred Famous Poems Card Game
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:41.54,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyakunin Isshu is a game where you listen to the reader's poem, then pick up the card with the last verse of the poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:43.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just have to pick up the card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.98,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Just like the boatman of the strait of Yura who lost his rudder and floats aimlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yura no to wo wataru funabito kadzi wo tae
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.44,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,the path that my love will take is unknown as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukue mo shiranu koi no michi ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I--Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.82,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine. It's New Year's anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.08,Signs,(19,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\c&H9BEF94&\bord3\shad0\an7\fnakbar\3c&H4E9E4D&\pos(219,1)}Japanese Badminton
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.51,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Hanetsuki" is Japanese Badminton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.51,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanetsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You hit the birdie with that paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:13.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop the birdie, you get punished by having your opponent scribble on your face with ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Well, let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.89,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more space to draw on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo! Yakumo, avenge your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.89,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a bad opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... You can't do anything well, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:37.61,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want to play too? I was hoping you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's Yakumo-chan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Wait a minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:58.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--We're switching players, too. Therefore, he can take the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:03.08,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why me? Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:09.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wonder who was the one who pushed me off a cliff on New Year's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, feel free to besmear him with ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--That's how it is, Imouto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.54,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she getting so desperate about against a underclassman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, Yakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting so worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.89,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Hige takes the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:42.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw then!
