Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:34.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's is all about swimsuit sumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:37.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Will girls really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet. You can expect to see lots of porori too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--Tougou?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:56.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. So this is sumo, a sport derived from a national sport symbolic of Japan's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The day this becomes an international sport comparable to soccer draws near!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce my passionate comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:09.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tennouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:12.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:17.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, release your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's is definitely about nothing but swimsuit sumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's...
